import { Component, Inject } from '@angular/core'; import { HttpClient } from '@angular/common/http'; @Component({ selector: 'app-fetch-houses', templateUrl: './fetch-houses.component.html' }) export class FetchHousesComponent { public houses: House[] = []; constructor(http: HttpClient, @Inject('BASE_URL') baseUrl: string) { http.get(baseUrl + 'house').subscribe(result => { this.houses = result; }, error => console.error(error)); } } interface Houses { number: number; names: string; attributes: string; planets: string; }
